data.description: Discover this inviting 3-bed, 2-bath ranch offering a seamless blend of charm and functionality. Enjoy main-level living enhanced by a spacious master ensuite with a new jetted tub, complemented by two roomy bedrooms and a full hall bath. The welcoming living room flows into a dining area, leading to an oversized private front deck and a serene back deck overlooking the pasture and two-stable barn. Unique ownership includes both sides of a flowing creek, adding natural beauty and recreational potential. Experience ease with no 4-wheel drive needed and no HOA fees. Additional features: durable metal roof, mature trees for privacy, and a versatile workspace in the walkout basement. Don't miss this opportunity for a tranquil yet modern lifestyle—schedule your viewing today!
